    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a reliable partner on the road. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can count on it for everything from daily commutes to fun weekend trips! It looks great, drives smoothly, and is just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel. If you're looking for a dependable ride that still feels fresh, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a test drive!",
