    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a Variable M Differential Lock, the chassis dynamics remain sharp and communicative. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the high-revving internals are track-ready. Equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable compression and rebound, this specimen offers a pure mechanical connection and a visceral induction note. A well-sorted driver\u2019s car for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
