    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved, super dependable, and runs like a charm! It\u2019s perfect if you're looking for a reliable set of wheels that still looks great on the road. It has plenty of life left and is ready for its next big adventure. Come take it for a spin, I think you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
