    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This BMW E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L high-compression inline-six features six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, providing a linear power delivery and a redline of 8,000 RPM. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a GKN limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal traction and engagement. The suspension architecture remains tight, utilizing aluminum lower control arms and a multi-link rear setup for precise turn-in and lateral stability. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and inspection of the rear subframe reinforcement points to ensure structural integrity under load. This vehicle represents a balanced driver\u2019s car with high mechanical fidelity, ready for the next enthusiast to exploit its balanced 50/50 weight distribution.",
